==English==
===Verb===
'''to circulate'''  (''intransitive'' or ''transitive'')
# to [[move]], or cause something to move, in [[circle]]s or through a [[circuit]]
# to move from [[person]] to person, as at a [[party]]
# to [[spread]] or [[disseminate]]
# to become [[widely]] [[known]]

